  (text "MCU: STM32G431CBT6, Phase-1 pin map + PB4 = DROOP_EN (NJTRST boot pull-up is\nbenign: SAFE state, output off). Shunt-region temperature = INA228 die temp\nregister - no third NTC pin needed. OUT_REQ stays on PB14; I2C on PA8/PA9\n(PB8 = BOOT0). Hot-swap health is inferred from AUX_PG (PGD gates the aux rail)."
    (at 15.24 33.02 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)))
    (uuid 15b15c6a-5aa8-4426-86f5-fefc0e6f4395)
  )

